{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_09_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 もう一度戦わせて下さい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "この間の、スタンプラリーをしながら街ブラする番組\nかなり好評らしい。頑張った甲斐があったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The program where you strolled around town doing a stamp rally\nseems to be quite popular. It was worth the effort.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　自分から企画を提案させてもらった\n番組が好評と聞くと、特別嬉しいですね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? It makes me especially happy to hear\nthat the show I proposed is well-received…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれを観て「うちの番組にもレギュラー出演を」って\n連絡もきてるんだ。この後、説明の時間をもらえるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After seeing that‚ we've been getting calls asking for a regular appearance.\nCan you make time to explain things to me after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.6166659992
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.6166659992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……ということなんだ。どうする？　俺としては正直\n最近沙季が受けている仕事が増え過ぎてないか心配でな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's what's going on. What do you think? To be honest‚\nI'm worried that Saki has been taking on too much work lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8666659992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は予定や体調の管理が抜群にうまい。ただ、学校や\nレッスンもあるし、これ以上は難しいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are exceptionally good at managing your schedule and health.\nBut you have school and lessons too. Wouldn't it be difficult to take on more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1999993325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.1333326658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですね……。本当にありがたいお話ですし\n出来れば受けたいところなんですが……やっぱり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yes… It's really a kind offer‚ and\nI'd like to take it on if possible‚ but… after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9333326658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.9999993325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしたんだ？　何か引っかかることがあるなら\n今のうちに言ってほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What's wrong? If there's something bothering you‚\nI want you to tell me now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2999993325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ちょっと、思い出していたんです\n{user}さんが以前、話してくれたことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I was just remembering\nwhat {user} told me before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.7999993325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺が話したこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I told you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7999993325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが脱退して、四人でアイドルを続けるか\nそれとも解散するか決断を迫られた時のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Kotono left‚ we were forced to decide whether\nto continue as a four-person idol group or disband.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1666659992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.0666659992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "「アイドルは限られた時間――青春を\n精一杯燃やして取り組むものだと思ってる」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I think being an idol is about making the most of a limited time―\nburning your youth as much as possible.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8666659992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "「だからこそ、一分一秒も無駄には出来ないし\n中途半端な覚悟でやってほしくないんだ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"That's why I can't waste a single second‚ and\nI don't want you to do it with half-hearted resolve.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8333326658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.7999993325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "あの時からその言葉を胸に\n一分一秒を無駄にしないように、全力でやってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since then‚ I've kept those words in my heart\nand have been doing my best so as not to waste a single second.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0999993325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.5666659992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、それでも時間自体には限りがあって\n迷わず進んでも、こぼれてしまうものもあるんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ even so‚ time itself is limited‚ and even if\nyou move forward without hesitation‚ some things will inevitably slip away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333326658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.7666685423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季のせいじゃないよ。みんなぶつかる壁だ。麻奈も\nそうだった。時間は有限で、全部やることは難しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not your fault‚ Saki. It's a wall that everyone runs into.\nMana did too. Time is limited‚ and it's hard to do everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666685423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "時には今回みたいに、選択を迫られることもある\nもちろん、迫られる選択は仕事のことだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ like this time‚ you may be forced to make a choice.\nOf course‚ the choices you're forced to make aren't just about work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1666685423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.333335209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でも私生活でもいい。迷った時は相談に乗るから\n……その上で、後悔しないように決断してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether it's about work or your personal life‚ I'll give you advice if you're ever unsure.\n…After that‚ I want you to make a decision you won't regret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.333335209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "後悔しないように……\nそうですね。ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A decision I won't regret…\nThat's right. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0000018757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.5666685423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "今、改めてお話を聞いて、自分がどう思ってるのか\nどういう決断をすべきなのか、分かった気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ after hearing you talk again‚ I think I realized\nwhat's in my mind‚ and what kind of decision I should make.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5666685423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "レギュラー番組のオファーをいただいたのは\n光栄ですし、心から嬉しく思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm honored and sincerely happy\nto receive a regular program offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2999998411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.0333331745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今回はお断りさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ please let me turn it down this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0333331745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、分かった。俺から連絡しておくよ\nじゃあ今日は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ okay. I'll contact them.\nWell then‚ today--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1333331745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 168.5333321572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "――{user}さん\nすみません。それと一つ、お願いがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "--{user}-san\nI'm sorry. But there's one thing I want to ask of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.2333331745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 175.3666654905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事とは直接関係がないかもしれませんし\nただ、困らせてしまうだけかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It may not be directly related to work‚ and\nit may just cause you trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8977429488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、ずっと言おうか迷っていました。今はもっと\n優先するべきことがあるって、自分に言い聞かせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I've been hesitant to say it. I kept telling myself that\nthere are more important things to prioritize right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7232676932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 193.1999988239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、アイドルとしての時間は限られているから……\n後悔したくないから。話しておこうと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ the time I have as an idol is limited…\nI don't want to regret it. So I'm going to talk about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.0333331745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 202.0666654905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nもう一度、サニーピースと戦わせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san\nPlease let me compete one more time with Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.7999998411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースと……沙季達、月のテンペストが戦う……\nNEXT VENUSグランプリの決勝みたいにか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace and… Saki and the others‚ Moon Tempest‚ competing…\nLike the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix final?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.3666665078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 217.6999988239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "サニピが私達をライバルだと思ってくれているように\n私達もずっと、サニピをライバルだと思っているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as Sunny Peace thinks of us as their rivals‚\nwe‚ too‚ have always thought of Sunny Peace as our rivals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.7628616094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、I-UNITYでスリクスに敗れてからは\nサニピと同じBIG4になって\nもう一度同じ舞台に立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why‚ ever since we lost to ⅢX at I-UNITY‚\nwe have wanted to become BIG4 like Sunny Peace‚\nand we have wanted to stand on the same stage once more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.8333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 235.5666654905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "そんな想いを抱いて\nどんな困難があろうとも、みんなで乗り越えてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With that thought in mind‚\nwe've overcome all kinds of difficulties together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.6666665078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 241.9333321572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "成長したのはサニピだけじゃありません。月ストだって\nどりきゅんとの戦いを通して殻を破ることが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just Sunny Peace that has grown. Moon Tempest\nwas able to break out of its shell through the battle with Dorikyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.5999998411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "今なら、あの時みたいな……いえ、あの時以上に\n最高のステージになると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ it would be like that time… no‚ even better than that time‚\nI think it would be the best stage ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.5333331745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 260.366659387
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、今の月ストとサニピがぶつかったら\nとてつもなく熱いステージになりそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the current Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace were to clash‚\nit would be an incredibly hot stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.1999937376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 267.266659387
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "本来は、ファンの皆さんや、オファーをくださる方々\nの期待に応えることを、何より優先するべきですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Originally‚ we should prioritize meeting the expectations\nof the fans and the people who give us offers‚ above all else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.0054674913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "でも、先程の{user}さんの言葉を聞いて\n私自身の想いも、口にしておきたくなったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ after hearing what {user}-san said earlier‚\nI wanted to express my own feelings‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.133327071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 282.6999927204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_02-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースを……千紗をそばで見ながら\nずっと胸の奥で育ててきた、この想いを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While watching Sunny Peace… while being by Chisa's side‚\nI've been nurturing this feeling deep in my heart all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.7,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}